# 0. Tong quan du an

## Muc tieu tong the
- [ ] Xay dung mot he thong web cho phep nguoi dung:
  - [ ] nhap cau hoi hoac noi long dang vuong
  - [ ] chon cach lap que
  - [ ] nhan ve que chinh
  - [ ] xem hao dong
  - [ ] xem que bien
  - [ ] doc loi giai ngan gon, de hieu
  - [ ] co mot huong nhin de suy ngam va ra quyet dinh binh tam hon

## Dinh huong san pham
- [ ] Dinh huong he thong theo tinh than:
  - [ ] de dung
  - [ ] de hieu
  - [ ] mang chat Viet
  - [ ] co cam giac tinh, sau, nhe
  - [ ] khong lam giao dien qua me tin hay qua roi mat
  - [ ] uu tien trai nghiem nguoi dung moi

## Pham vi giai doan 1
- [ ] Giai doan 1 chi can co:
  - [ ] 1 trang chu
  - [ ] 1 khu vuc nhap cau hoi
  - [ ] 1 khu vuc chon phuong phap lap que
  - [ ] 1 nut de bat dau lap que
  - [ ] 1 API xu ly
  - [ ] 1 bo du lieu co ban
  - [ ] 1 khu vuc hien thi ket qua
- [ ] Chua can:
  - [ ] dang nhap
  - [ ] dang ky
  - [ ] thanh toan
  - [ ] AI phuc tap
  - [ ] admin phuc tap
  - [ ] app mobile rieng
  - [ ] da ngon ngu
  - [ ] database phuc tap neu chua can

