# 31. Ke hoach commit hang ngay

## Nguyen tac
- [ ] Moi ngay chi can xong 1 task nho
- [ ] Moi ngay it nhat 1 commit
- [ ] Moi commit phai ro rang
- [ ] Sau commit thi push

## Vi du task nho de commit
- [ ] Sua README
- [ ] Them 1 component
- [ ] Them 1 file du lieu
- [ ] Them 1 function
- [ ] Them 1 doan copywriting
- [ ] Chinh 1 man hinh mobile
- [ ] Sua 1 loi

## Mau commit message
- [ ] `add initial README`
- [ ] `add detailed project todo list`
- [ ] `initialize Next.js app`
- [ ] `add homepage scaffold`
- [ ] `add question form component`
- [ ] `add fortune API route`
- [ ] `implement coin divination logic`
- [ ] `display result card`
- [ ] `add local history storage`
- [ ] `refine landing page copy`

